Fix semconv schema URL conflict with otel SDK v1.43.0.

The otel SDK v1.43.0 aligns with semconv v1.40.0, but grafana-agent imports
semconv v1.24.0. When both are used in resource.New(), the conflicting
schema URLs cause resource detection to fail. Update the import to match
the SDK's semconv version.

diff --git a/internal/flow/tracing/tracing.go b/internal/flow/tracing/tracing.go
index cd7acd8..676ba61 100644
--- a/internal/flow/tracing/tracing.go
+++ b/internal/flow/tracing/tracing.go
@@ -14,7 +14,7 @@ import (
 	"go.opentelemetry.io/otel/exporters/otlp/otlptrace"
 	"go.opentelemetry.io/otel/sdk/resource"
 	tracesdk "go.opentelemetry.io/otel/sdk/trace"
-	semconv "go.opentelemetry.io/otel/semconv/v1.24.0"
+	semconv "go.opentelemetry.io/otel/semconv/v1.40.0"
 	"go.opentelemetry.io/otel/trace"
 )
 
